<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Business Inquiry Received - CodeSmith InfoSoft LLP</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body style="padding-top: 40px; padding-bottom: 40px; font-family: 'Georgia', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding: 40px 0; background-color: #f4f6f9;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="700" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
          style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow: hidden;">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px 40px; color: #333;">
              <!-- <div style="text-align: center;">
                <img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/code_smith.png" alt="CodeSmith InfoSoft Logo" />
              </div> -->
              <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                <div style="
      background-image: url('<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/code_smith.png');
      background-size: contain;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: center;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
      height: 150px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: inline-block;">
                </div>
              </div>
              <h2 style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 30px; color: #119448; text-align: center;">
                Thank You for Reaching Out!
              </h2>

              <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hi <strong>
                  <%= data.fullName %>
                </strong>,</p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                We’ve successfully received your business inquiry and are thrilled about your interest in
                <strong>CodeSmith InfoSoft LLP</strong>. Our dedicated team is currently reviewing the details you
                shared,
                and you can expect a response from us within the next 24 hours.
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                In the meantime, feel free to explore our past projects, services, and client testimonials to learn how
                we've helped businesses like yours succeed in the digital world.
              </p>

              <hr style="border: none; height: 1px; background-color: #e1e1e1; margin: 30px 0;" />

              <h3 style="font-size: 18px; color: #273974; margin-bottom: 15px;">Here’s a summary of your inquiry:</h3>

              <!-- Inquiry Summary Table -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="12" cellspacing="0"
                style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px;">
                <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
                  <td style="font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Name:</td>
                  <td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
                    <%= data.fullName %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Email:</td>
                  <td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
                    <%= data.email %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Phone:</td>
                  <td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
                    <%= data.mobile %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-weight: bold; vertical-align: top;">Message:</td>
                  <td>
                    <%= data.message %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- CTA -->
              <div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                  Curious to learn how we can boost your business with digital solutions?
                </p>
                <a href="https://codesmithinfosoft.com" target="_blank"
                  style="display: inline-block; background-color: #119448; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none;">
                  <img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/web.png" alt="Website Icon" width="18" height="18"
                    style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" />
                  <strong style="font-weight: 600;">Visit Our Website</strong>
                </a>
              </div>

              <!-- Closing -->
              <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                Thank you again for connecting with us. We look forward to the opportunity to work together.<br /><br />
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Best regards,<br />
                <strong>Team CodeSmith InfoSoft LLP</strong>
              </p>
              <!-- </td>
          </tr> -->

              <!-- Footer -->
              <!-- <tr style="background-color: #273974;">
            <td align="center" style="color: #fff;"> -->
              <div style=" text-align: center; background-color: #273974; padding: 20px 0; margin-top: 20px;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #fff;">&copy; 2021 CodeSmith InfoSoft LLP. All
                  rights
                  reserved.</p>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/codesmithinfosoft" target="_blank"
                  style="margin: 0 8px; display: inline-block;">
                  <img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/insta.png" alt="Instagram" width="24" style="display: block;" />
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/codesmithinfosoftllp" target="_blank"
                  style="margin: 0 8px; display: inline-block;">
                  <img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/linkedin.png" alt="LinkedIn" width="24"
                    style="display: block;" />
                </a>
                <a href="https://x.com/CodeSmithSHG" target="_blank" style="margin: 0 8px; display: inline-block;">
                  <img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/twitter.png" alt="X" width="24" style="display: block;" />
                </a>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>